description: Alexa will give you definitions of some terms and components of basic electronics and you answer with the name of the term or component. Alexa will give you 7 definitions and you get 1 point for each correct answer. To get started just say start new game.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask electronics flash cards to start new game
name: electronics flash cards
shortDescription: Electronic components and terms can be tough to remember. Use this skill to quiz yourself on basic electronics.
